item.title: How Do i Change It So That When i Cut Trees It Gives Me Logs Not Money!
item.dc:creator: @mrdek11 mrdek11
item.description:
@mrdek11 wrote:

Find the void that handles chopping trees, and you’ll see something like this:

addItem(995, 1);

Change the 995 to whatever item number your logs are.
(Sorry I’d be more specific, but I’ve never seen a server give money instead of logs.)
